We live in a decent area of southwest Florida. We rent the back half of a duplex. There's 4 parking spots in the front of the house, 2 for us, 2 for the neighbors. They have 5 cars parked up there all the time! I think multiple families live there. 99% sure they're all illegal. My landlord lives in Canada and has a realtor handle his rental properties. I don't think he would care anyways as long as he's collecting his rent every month.

It's really infuriating. I know they lied on their lease. No way it's legal to have that many people living in an 1800 square foot unit. 

Here I am with my family squeezing by, and theres 2 younger pregnant women and each of their families living next store.

Yes, I'm that bitch. I would call ICE on them, I just don't know how I could prove it or if my anonymous tip would even be considered. And I don't think my landlord really cares. He probably prefers illegals. 

Open to suggestions...
